com.ceteva.forms.views

Class FormTreeEditListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ceteva.forms.views.FormTreeEditListener

  • public class FormTreeEditListener
extends java.lang.Object
    The listener interface for receiving formTreeEdit events. The class that is interested in processing a formTreeEdit event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addFormTreeEditListener method. When the formTreeEdit event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
    See Also:
    FormTreeEditEvent
